              },
              "free_text": [
                " ERROR ON THE EXPERIMENTAL VALUES WAS DERIVED",
                " TAKING INTO ACCOUNT THE ERROR (IN PERCENT) ON",
                " -THE TOTAL NEUTRON FLUX (ABOUT 3PERCENT)",
                " -THE ABSOLUTE GAMMA ACTIVITY OF THE PRODUCTS",
